  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the horror mansion in the forest! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to get out of here? Maybe you can save someone else in the process? Or, on the contrary, will you become a cold-blooded killer? It all depends only on you and your decisions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511340/extras/d7339acc2567fdc89357aab203bf644b.poster.avif?t=1741906912\" width=500 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511340/extras/d7339acc2567fdc89357aab203bf644b.webm?t=1741906912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511340/extras/d7339acc2567fdc89357aab203bf644b.mp4?t=1741906912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 unique endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gloomy atmosphere with a bit of post-irony</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Difficult, but at the same time fair tests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Riddles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partial destructibility</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of interactive items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A weapon with which you can fight back the Creature</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random generation of some items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss fight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dialogue system</p></li></ul>",
